-- San Diego Padres Owners Hire Allen & Co. to Advise on Team Sale
-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 2012-04-10T22:47:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-10/san-diego-padres-owners-hire-allen-co-to-advise-on-team-sale.html
The  San Diego Padres ’ owners hired
bankers Allen & Co. and Moag & Co. to sell the team.  The process may take several months, Padres Chairman John
Moores said today in a  statement  posted on the team’s website.  The Los Angeles Times reported on April 7 that the
ownership group had hired Allen & Co.’s Steve Greenberg as an
adviser, citing people familiar with the situation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andy Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
